$ CSS: font property
@ font

The `font` allows to combine the values of a few font related properties:
  • `font-style`
  • `font-variant`
  • `font-weight`
  • `font-stretch`
  • `line-height`
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/font/size[`font-size`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/font-family[`font-family`]

sa:

  → development/web/CSS/properties

  The `font` property of the `→ development/web/HTML/tags/canvas/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D` object.
